data.description: Charming 3 Bed and 1 Bath Split Level style residence. This home is in need of some TLC, so bring your ideas and get ready to make this space your own! Listing price is approved SS - with appraised value $450k (see attachments).  Located in a sought-after Blauvelt location, it is close to public transportation, great schools, post office, library, shopping, parks and recreation. It is also convenient to highways for an easy Commute to Westchester, New Jersey, and is just 30 min NYC. Don't miss out on this great opportunity!
